---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About | Amaljith Kuttamath" description="AI Engineer researching LLM trust, safety, and mechanistic interpretability. Building tooling for model evaluation and failure mode analysis.">
  <article class="about-content animate-in">
    <h1>About</h1>

    <section class="about-section">
      <p>
        I research how language models fail and build tooling to measure it. Right now that means <strong>Trust Bench</strong>, a framework for profiling LLM trustworthiness: extracting internal signals, evaluating across safety dimensions, and diagnosing failure modes specific to a deployment context. Before that, I spent years building retrieval pipelines and knowledge graphs for healthcare, where I developed methodology for measuring hallucination patterns in retrieval-augmented generation. That work is what pulled me toward the deeper question of what's actually happening inside these models.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What I Work On</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="focus-list">
        <li><strong>LLM trust and safety:</strong> failure mode analysis, hallucination detection, mechanistic interpretability</li>
        <li><strong>Evaluation systems:</strong> building frameworks that profile model behavior beyond standard benchmarks</li>
        <li><strong>Retrieval and knowledge:</strong> RAG pipelines, knowledge graphs, measuring retrieval fidelity</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Background</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="background-brief">Started at <a href="https://www.isro.gov.in" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ISRO</a>. Co-founded <strong>RadianArc</strong>, where we built digital twins for predictive maintenance on industrial machinery. MS in Data Analytics from George Mason University, where my thesis focused on RAG systems for healthcare.</p>
      <div class="credentials">
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Cert</span>
          <span class="detail-value">Google Cloud Professional ML Engineer, 2024</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
          <span class="detail-label">Paper</span>
          <span class="detail-value"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1097/QMH.0000000000000525" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Predicting Risk of Lung Cancer</a>, Quality Management in Health Care</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-section about-cta">
      <p>
        Want to collaborate or talk shop? <a href="mailto:kuttamath.amaljith@gmail.com">kuttamath.amaljith@gmail.com</a> · <a href="/resume.pdf" class="resume-link">Resume (PDF)</a>
      </p>
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/amaljithkuttamath" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/amaljithk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/amaljithkm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a>
        <a href="https://substack.com/@amaljithk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Substack</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "ProfilePage",
    "mainEntity": {
      "@type": "Person",
      "name": "Amaljith Kuttamath",
      "jobTitle": "AI Engineer",
      "url": "https://amaljithkuttamath.github.io",
      "email": "kuttamath.amaljith@gmail.com",
      "alumniOf": [
        { "@type": "CollegeOrUniversity", "name": "George Mason University" },
        { "@type": "CollegeOrUniversity", "name": "GITAM University" }
      ],
      "sameAs": [
        "https://github.com/amaljithkuttamath",
        "https://linkedin.com/in/amaljithk",
        "https://x.com/amaljithkm",
        "https://substack.com/@amaljithk"
      ]
    }
  })} />
</Base>

<style>
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .focus-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .focus-list li {
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .background-brief {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .credentials {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .credentials .detail-row {
    padding: var(--space-xs) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--fg-faint);
  }

  .credentials .detail-row:first-child {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--fg-faint);
  }

  .credentials .detail-value a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--fg-faint);
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
  }

  .credentials .detail-value a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-decoration-color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .about-cta p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .social-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .social-links a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-label);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    transition: color var(--duration) var(--ease);
  }

  .social-links a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }
</style>
